 class AORSplitter
          Generates from each feature f_i up to five new features {f_i(a), f_i(ao), f_i(o), f_i(or), f_i(r)} responding to Attack/Onset/Release information: f_i(a) saves only f_i values from the beginnings of the attack intervals f_i(ao) from the middle of the attack interval f_i(o) from the onset window f_i(or) from the middle of the release interval f_i(r) from the end of the release interval
